{"tid":2285444,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"袁國勇：估計香港140萬人感染並不誇張","createTime":"2020-11-14T06:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T13:26:36.000Z","uid":237459,"like":11,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"75a4c71cfaa59552e7ebfd713b5ffd564164868f","tid":2285444,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T06:06:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇認為，香港隔離設施不足，無可避免要對內地抵港人士實施14日家居隔離，除了靠巿民自律，亦要靠政府各部門一同執法。他又認為，新型冠狀病毒傳播性高，估計全港有一百四十萬人感染有科學基礎。<br />\n<br />\n港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇：「新型病毒傳播是非常之有效率，根本與流感，特別是抗原漂移的流感是一模一樣，所以我絕對不覺得我所說是誇張了，很多人罵我，但我不理，事實歸事實，大家要看科學，不要看感覺。若香港不採取所有切實可行措施，不完全落實措施，香港可以成為任何一個內地城市，有爆發地方一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=379549\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379549&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNywfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=133e4c82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D379549&h=3e38dc2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=379549</a>"},{"pid":"c977ece756343ab1c27f2ce2f89ccde981c9479c","tid":2285444,"uid":182653,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"又出黎誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348538eae8dbf2ee4df1841d94b29cc0bc7d24a5","tid":2285444,"uid":29917,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T06:07:28.000Z","msg":"去左歐洲變左種，宜家唔係武漢當初果隻病毒"},{"pid":"e0e67dfec3ceeb6dc2a6be1c23697adfe3a64bfc","tid":2285444,"uid":23160,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"140萬人中左姐係有病同冇病冇分別啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad9dc8a93cffc8d6d7c59f74af0b213c700125a","tid":2285444,"uid":15356,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T06:08:04.